events.name: Amped UP!
events.description: Challenge the brothers of Nu Delta to videogames, ping pong, pool, foosball, or anything you can think of to win a brand new TV, all while enjoying food from some of our favorite restaurants delivered fresh throughout the day!

events.name: Southern Style Chicken & Waffles
events.description: Swing by Nu Delta for some southern style chicken and waffles, and some homemade smoothies to go with them!

events.name: Jet Skis
events.description: Drive jet skis with the brothers of Nu Delta! Race and get air off some waves on the open ocean!

events.name: Paintball
events.description: See if you can keep up with the brothers of Nu Delta in this all out paint war at Boston Paintball!

events.name: Monster Jam!
events.description: Stop by Nu Delta's Monster Jam to see why our parties are sponsored by Monster. Grab a few cans to refuel, then get ready to dance all night!

events.name: Firing Range
events.description: Fire some crazy big guns at the firing range with Nu Delta and see if your videogame skills translate to the real deal!

events.name: SkyZone
events.description: Join Nu Delta in playing dodgeball and basketball on the trampoline floors at SkyZone! Try to keep up and get your appetite ready for Steak and Lobster!!

events.name: Steak & Lobster
events.description: Stop by for some delicious steak & lobster at Nu Delta, meet some brothers and see our awesome 4-story Back Bay home!

events.name: Target Runs
events.description: Need some last-minute school supplies, or just want to go shopping? Nu Delta's got you covered. We'll be making runs to target or (almost) anywhere else you need to go for those last-minute supplies.

events.name: Rockbed BBQ
events.description: Nothing beats a good burger on Nu Delta's iconic Phoenix Rock Garden with great music and the brothers of Nu Delta! Come see our house and meet some awesome people!

events.name: Dick's Last Resort
events.description: Experience the outrageousness of the Dick's Last Resort restaurant in downtown Boston with Nu Delta while enjoying delicious barbecue and american-style cuisine.
